description.narrative: Good progress despite ongoing COVID-19 pandemic. Updated global database on WASH in households leading to significant increase in number of countries with recent estimates for SDG indicators. Expanded database on inequalities to include estimates disaggregated by wealth quintile and sub-national region for >100 countries. Published global progress update on WASH in households taking stock of progress over first 5 years of the SDG period (special focus on fragile contexts and impact of COVID-19). Provided data and analysis for global flagship report on State of the World’s Hand Hygiene.; | Status:On-track | As-of Date:27/03/2022
